  <p>config = AnalysisConfig() config.psf_file =
  “martini_membrane_system.psf” # Martini topology config.xtc_file =
  “production_10us.xtc” # 10 microsecond CG trajectory
  config.contact_cutoff = 10.0 # Appropriate for Martini beads</p>
</sec>
<sec id="define-competing-tm-interfaces-residue-numbers-mapped-to-cg-beads">
