  <p>config.add_region(“TM_N_term”, resid_start=645, resid_end=655,
  description=“N-terminal interface (GxxxG motif)”)
  config.add_region(“TM_C_term”, resid_start=656, resid_end=671,
  description=“C-terminal interface”)</p>
</sec>
<sec id="temperature-factor-for-martini-optional">
  <title>Temperature factor for Martini (optional)</title>
  <p>config.temperature_factor = 2.5 # Accounts for accelerated
  dynamics</p>
</sec>
<sec id="run-analysis">
  <title>Run analysis</title>
  <p>results = run_full_analysis(config)</p>
</sec>
